metadata.name: An Eclipse
metadata.description:
2007: Hospitalized for Anorexia at age 14 during first month of high school; refused treatment.

2008: Mindset change leads to unexpected turnaround and subsequent recovery; asked to give a speech to patients and families at NEDAwareness Week (02.25.08)
